snippet.title: BlackThorne Keep - Pre Alpha Quest - Wings of Stone
snippet.description:
Heres some pre alpha footage of one of the early quests in the single player/coop campaign. It is EARLY stages implementation, just a performance test for now. Enjoy!

"Thommas BlackThorne follows the Rogue Soldiers to the valley of hawks in hopes to find the elder that they kidnapped unharmed. The Rogue Commander intends to find some kind of treasure at the forgotten temple and believes that the elder can help him with it. "
